      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait really?? that sounds so extreme. i barely even have a fever and i can still walk around, it just hurts when i move certain ways. i've had cramps like this before and they always go away with some strong meds. are you sure it's not just something I ate? i'm kinda scared to go to the er if it's just gas, it's so expensive and i don't want to go through all that trouble if i can just fix it at home. can't i just take some tylenol and see how i feel in the morning?",
